If you work all day in apps like Spreadsheets, Docs, Drive and others, then this extension will save you time and effort by putting links to these apps right on your new tab page. New Tab searches will be provided by Yahoo!®

By clicking on the "Add to Chrome" button, I accept and
agree to installing the ‘App Start Tab’ Chrome extension and setting Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service, New Tab search powered by Yahoo!®, and to the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

For more information, please visit:
Privacy Policy: https://appstarttab.com/privacy-policy/
Terms of Use: https://appstarttab.com/terms-of-service/
Uninstall Information: https://appstarttab.com/uninstall/
